	<h3>FISD Member Search</h3>
<hr>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.692em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1a1a1a;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border: 0px !important; font-style: inherit !important; font-variant: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; font-stretch: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px;">Looking for someone you met at a FISD event? Trying to track down the "right" person at a FISD member company?<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">
